Entries.default: "The body was a decoy. This does not bode well."
"Don't suppose anyone cares to go fishing?"
"Ishi, please stop eating the worms. Please."
"Gods, cap. Can't say I were expecting the sad bastard to be a bucket of fish bait."
"I too would wear a mask if I was made of worms."
"Sakes alive, Watcher. I ain't never seen a wizard made of nightcrawlers before."
"A remote corporeal projection. Which means the wizard is still out there."
"Heh. We are all worms sooner or later."
